{
  "stem": "14897.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have the sense of power if you can grant life as well as deny it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that seems to be how human nature often reacts to such-- I've seen such situations over and over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not the only such situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, the selections went on for about two or three months like that, in a-- in a kind of organized manner, but block by block.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just about, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Constantly frightened, very depressed, with a sense of hopelessness, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with very little to distract you from that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you looked-- on a day where you-- where you were safe, you looked for some distractions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You tried to read something, to think about other things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By this time, shortage of food, of course, so you're-- you're hungry a lot of the time, so you think a lot about food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You think about the lack of body comforts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You think about friends, some of whom I never-- most of whom I never saw again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very difficult three months, really extremely difficult, culminated in a big action, which was, by the way, described in a-- in a novel about the ghetto by Leon Uris called [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was an action in which all the Jews of the ghetto were forced to go into a small section of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By this time, of course, probably about 2/3 of the population of the ghetto had been transported and exterminated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were there for two or three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And out of that little section, only people with papers, official papers, were allowed to come out.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
